n  - Reads version from `.cloche/version` file (lines 961-968)\n  - **Fetches git commit history** using `git log` (line 989):\n    ```go\n    cmd := exec.Command(\"git\", \"log\", \"--follow\", \"--format=%H %aI %s\", \"--\", relPath)\n    ```\n    Returns: commit SHA, date, and message for each prompt file\n\n- **`handleAPIPromptDiff()`** (lines 1027-1056): Fetches file diffs between commits\n  - Uses `git diff` command (line 1047): \n    ```go\n    cmd := exec.Command(\"git\", \"diff\", sha+\"^..\"+sha, \"--\", file)\n    ```\n  - Returns diff output as plain text\n\n- **`handleAPIStepContent()`** (lines 1134-1199): Fetches step content from files or inline config\n  - Reads prompt files (line 1178)\n  - Reads script files (lines 1189-1196)\n  - Returns file contents as plain text\n\n### 4. **Frontend JavaScript Logic** (`/workspace/internal/adapters/web/templates/project_detail.html` lines 89-139)\n\n**Key Functions:**\n\n- **`loadProjectInfo()`** (lines 89-121): Calls API to load project info and renders HTML with:\n  - Docker image and version metadata\n  - Prompt files with commit history in expandable sections\n  \n- **`toggleDiff()`** (lines 123-139): Handles clicking on commit entries\n  - Fetches the git diff from the API\n  - Inserts a `<pre class=\"diff-block\">` element below the clicked entry\n  - Can toggle the diff on/off by clicking again\n\n### 5. **Styling** (`/workspace/internal/adapters/web/static/style.css` lines 197-221)\n\n```css\ndetails {\n    margin: 0.5rem 0;\n}\n\ndetails summary {\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n}\n\ndetails pre {\n    background: var(--bg-surface);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    padding: 0.75rem;\n    /* ... overflow and text styling ... */\n}\n```\n\nAlso styles the diff block:\n```css\n.diff-block {\n    background: var(--bg);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    /* ... styling for diffs ... */\n}\n```\n\n### File Paths Summary\n\n- **Web Handler (API endpoints)**: `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler.go`\n- **Project Detail Template**: `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/templates/project_detail.html`\n- **Styling**: `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/static/style.css`\n- **Layout Template**: `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/templates/layout.html`"}],"totalDurationMs":27974,"totalTokens":51023,"totalToolUseCount":20,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":283,"cache_read_input_tokens":49663,"output_tokens":1073,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":283},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
